sourcesContent: import Container from '@material-ui/core/Container' import Typography from '@material-ui/core/Typography' import { Button } from '@material-ui/core' import Link from '@material-ui/core/Link' export default function Index() { return ( <> Can't Stop Us Toolkit Can’t Stop Columbus is a community-wide movement that activates our city’s talents and compassion to solve real problems. We embrace courageous ideas and rapidly deliver new and innovative solutions. We built this toolkit to help organize the movement in other cities. The purpose of this toolkit is: To help other communities kickstart support movements like Can’t Stop Columbus To empower organizers to inspire an attitude of help and support To provide a structure for creating a movement by sharing tools, insights, successes, and failures ); }
